- cs.CY (Computers and Society): The paper discusses the potential impact of automated speech analysis on the study of human thought and mental health, which could be relevant to the sub-category of computers and society.
- cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing): While not the most likely category, the focus on analyzing speech and emotional intensity could also be relevant to the sub-category of sound and music computing.
